#### Keybindings

# Forward movement
bind Next      next
bind Return    next
bind Right     next
bind space     next
bind Down      nextOverlay
bind S+Next    next10
bind S+Return  next10
bind S+Right   next10
bind S+space   next10
bind S+Down    next10

# Back movement
bind Left      prev
bind Prior     prev
bind Up        prevOverlay
bind S+Left    prev10
bind S+Prior   prev10
bind S+Up      prev10

# "Jumps"
bind Home      gotoFirst
bind End       gotoLast
bind g         goto
bind Tab       overview
bind BackSpace histBack

# Exit
#bind Escape    quit
bind Escape    exitState
bind q         quit

# Timer related
bind s         start
bind p         pause
bind r         resetTimer
bind R         reset

# Change state
bind b         blank
bind period    blank
bind f         freeze

# Presentation properties
bind n         note
bind o         overlay
bind e         endSlide

#### Mouse bindings
mouse 1        next
mouse S+1      next10
mouse 2        overview
mouse 3        prev
mouse S+3      prev10
